          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-818A703C-line-1" n="1">In your Indignation what Mercy appears?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818A703C-line-2" n="2">While Ionothan's threatn'd with Loss of \<hi rend="italics">del</hi>·your\his Ears:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818A703C-line-3" n="3">For who woud not think it, a much better Choice;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818A703C-line-4" n="4">By your Knife to be mangled, then wreck'd by y<hi rend="superscript">ṛ</hi> Voice:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818A703C-line-5" n="5">If you woud be truly reveng'd on the Parson,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818A703C-line-6" n="6">Command his Attendance while you act the Farce-on:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818A703C-line-7" n="7">Instead of your maiming, your shooting or Banging,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818A703C-line-8" n="8">Bid Povey secure him, while Kite is Haranguing:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818A703C-line-9" n="9">Had this been your Method to torture him, long-since</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-818A703C-line-10" n="10">He had cut his Own Ears, to be rid of your Nonsense.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
